            </p>
            <p class="clearfix">
                <span class="font_s14 fl">积分抵扣：</span><span class="color_orange font_s18 fr">￥@Model.IntegralMoney</span>
            </p>
            <p class="clearfix">
                <span class="font_s14 fl">优惠券：</span><span class="color_orange font_s18 fr">￥@Model.CouponMoney</span>
            </p>
